27DtlsTransportState TranslateState(cricket::DtlsTransportState internal_state) {
28 switch (internal_state) {
29 case cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_NEW:
30 return DtlsTransportState::kNew;
31 case cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_CONNECTING:
32 return DtlsTransportState::kConnecting;
33 case cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_CONNECTED:
34 return DtlsTransportState::kConnected;
35 case cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_CLOSED:
36 return DtlsTransportState::kClosed;
37 case cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_FAILED:
38 return DtlsTransportState::kFailed;
39 }
40 RTC_CHECK_NOTREACHED();
41}
42
43} // namespace
44
45// Implementation of DtlsTransportInterface
46DtlsTransport::DtlsTransport(
47 std::unique_ptr<cricket::DtlsTransportInternal> internal)
48 : owner_thread_(rtc::Thread::Current()),
49 info_(DtlsTransportState::kNew),
50 internal_dtls_transport_(std::move(internal)),
51 ice_transport_(rtc::make_ref_counted<IceTransportWithPointer>(
52 internal_dtls_transport_->ice_transport())) {
53 RTC_DCHECK(internal_dtls_transport_.get());
54 internal_dtls_transport_->SubscribeDtlsState(
55 [this](cricket::DtlsTransportInternal* transport,
56 cricket::DtlsTransportState state) {
57 OnInternalDtlsState(transport, state);
58 });
59 UpdateInformation();
60}
61
62DtlsTransport::~DtlsTransport() {
63 // We depend on the signaling thread to call Clear() before dropping
64 // its last reference to this object.
65 RTC_DCHECK(owner_thread_->IsCurrent() || !internal_dtls_transport_);
66}
67
68DtlsTransportInformation DtlsTransport::Information() {
69 MutexLock lock(&lock_);
70 return info_;
71}
72
73void DtlsTransport::RegisterObserver(DtlsTransportObserverInterface* observer) {
74 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
75 RTC_DCHECK(observer);
76 observer_ = observer;
77}
78
79void DtlsTransport::UnregisterObserver() {
80 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
81 observer_ = nullptr;
82}
83
84rtc::scoped_refptr<IceTransportInterface> DtlsTransport::ice_transport() {
85 return ice_transport_;
86}
87
88// Internal functions
89void DtlsTransport::Clear() {
90 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
91 RTC_DCHECK(internal());
92 bool must_send_event =
93 (internal()->dtls_state() != cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_CLOSED);
94 // The destructor of cricket::DtlsTransportInternal calls back
95 // into DtlsTransport, so we can't hold the lock while releasing.
96 std::unique_ptr<cricket::DtlsTransportInternal> transport_to_release;
97 {
98 MutexLock lock(&lock_);
99 transport_to_release = std::move(internal_dtls_transport_);
100 ice_transport_->Clear();
101 }
102 UpdateInformation();
103 if (observer_ && must_send_event) {
104 observer_->OnStateChange(Information());
105 }
106}
107
108void DtlsTransport::OnInternalDtlsState(
109 cricket::DtlsTransportInternal* transport,
110 cricket::DtlsTransportState state) {
111 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
112 RTC_DCHECK(transport == internal());
113 RTC_DCHECK(state == internal()->dtls_state());
114 UpdateInformation();
115 if (observer_) {
116 observer_->OnStateChange(Information());
117 }
118}
119
120void DtlsTransport::UpdateInformation() {
121 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
122 MutexLock lock(&lock_);
123 if (internal_dtls_transport_) {
124 if (internal_dtls_transport_->dtls_state() ==
125 cricket::DTLS_TRANSPORT_CONNECTED) {
126 bool success = true;
127 int ssl_cipher_suite;
128 int tls_version;
129 int srtp_cipher;
130 success &= internal_dtls_transport_->GetSslVersionBytes(&tls_version);
131 success &= internal_dtls_transport_->GetSslCipherSuite(&ssl_cipher_suite);
132 success &= internal_dtls_transport_->GetSrtpCryptoSuite(&srtp_cipher);
133 if (success) {
134 info_ = DtlsTransportInformation(
135 TranslateState(internal_dtls_transport_->dtls_state()), tls_version,
136 ssl_cipher_suite, srtp_cipher,
137 internal_dtls_transport_->GetRemoteSSLCertChain());
138 } else {
139 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "DtlsTransport in connected state has incomplete "
140 "TLS information";
141 info_ = DtlsTransportInformation(
142 TranslateState(internal_dtls_transport_->dtls_state()),
143 absl::nullopt, absl::nullopt, absl::nullopt,
144 internal_dtls_transport_->GetRemoteSSLCertChain());
145 }
146 } else {
147 info_ = DtlsTransportInformation(
148 TranslateState(internal_dtls_transport_->dtls_state()));
149 }
150 } else {
151 info_ = DtlsTransportInformation(DtlsTransportState::kClosed);
152 }
153}
